snippet.title: Snacktorio - Demo Coming Soon!
snippet.description:
A teaser of our newest game, Snacktorio - a factory cooking sim game where you must satisfy the appetites of unspeakable horrors... with food!

Build and manage sprawling networks of machines + pipes to mass produce delicious meals that can satiate the endless hunger of the beasts that are invading your home. Order Up!
